{"tid":1850824,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我好似係性單戀","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T09:08:14.000Z","uid":243601,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"d15b1918d3796550164b8ce8bea713b26c20bd8d","tid":1850824,"uid":243601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"同ex拍左兩年拖，分左手差唔多一年<br />\n<br />\n呢一年都有對過人有好感，但當feel到佢好似都有少少鍾意自己既時候，就會覺得「屌條友係咪有病，點解對我有好感」「喂，唔好鍾意我啦」，然後婉拒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之就係對佢有feel但唔想佢鍾意番我，當佢鍾意我既時候我會好抗拒，好似已經鍾意唔到人咁<br />\n<br />\n上網search過話呢啲係性單戀既表現，係性向既一種，但又有人話算係心理病（但我又未係好嚴重）<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好困擾，因為好似每次就快可以有結果既時候我都親手推開左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪有病，使唔使睇睇心理醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ee92a85f0bc7c87d69aee571c6646b7ed9d27d","tid":1850824,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"咩叫性單戀"},{"pid":"20bee790dff79ae65f98033eb4213640e4e715a1","tid":1850824,"uid":347110,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"e0ee92a85f0bc7c87d69aee571c6646b7ed9d27d","tid":1850824,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"咩叫性單戀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"樓主想表示嘅應該係佢鍾意鍾意人 但係唔鍾意人地鍾意佢😂"},{"pid":"aa74eec3a683f0ed120c7fecea7114755a434dc9","tid":1850824,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"可能太自卑？"},{"pid":"25ab7f7462e0841f419921c94121247319d397ea","tid":1850824,"uid":243601,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"e0ee92a85f0bc7c87d69aee571c6646b7ed9d27d","tid":1850824,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"咩叫性單戀"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:43:30.000Z","msg":"性單戀（英語：Lithromantic）指對某人產生好感，卻不希望從對方獲得情感回應的人。因此，這類族群的戀愛情節可能會因對方做了情感回應而消失。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7595927540e2986f0181a8a6edfe7f9cfd0f41f","tid":1850824,"uid":200360,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed6e71078eda9670bcb7b025e6d00da77faca5e","tid":1850824,"uid":326777,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:46:34.000Z","msg":"甚至會覺得嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79676dcaedef6498d63bf3d912ab07b3718c1f12","tid":1850824,"uid":243601,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"aa74eec3a683f0ed120c7fecea7114755a434dc9","tid":1850824,"uid":82344,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"可能太自卑？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:47:41.000Z","msg":"可能係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日都覺得自己唔夠好、無優點<br />\n睇下點解決啦，啲人叫你love yourself more，玩咩大佬，我而家就係love唔撚到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cb13208e75d1036df4bc49aba6b4f066b64630","tid":1850824,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9ba59fff518080c5e5615068db1f4a97418ce11","tid":1850824,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:48:49.000Z","msg":"lithromantic即係收兵"},{"pid":"2e3caa988aecea853fc2373ade0cc45a80e9cbec","tid":1850824,"uid":239615,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:54:13.000Z","msg":"係心理病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你係下意識怕某啲事會發生"},{"pid":"8bc7511efbdab82d15545fb766839e0fb8dca898","tid":1850824,"uid":243601,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b7595927540e2986f0181a8a6edfe7f9cfd0f41f","tid":1850824,"uid":200360,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets